’Щ@fc885acbdbb20f6aa797fdc2e674a8dc2ab1612ed0cfe29c2a3a9931c6c71983Ъ›Title: title: polars concat
Path: Flags
Content:
``--no-parallel``
: Disable parallel execution.
``--rechunk``
: Rechunk the resulting dataframe.
``--to-supertypes``
: Cast to supertypes.
``--diagonal``
: Concatenate dataframes diagonally.
``--no-maintain-order``
: Do not maintain order. The default behavior is to maintain order.
``--from-partitioned-ds``
: Concatenate dataframes from a partitioned dataset.
